            <title>联想 ThinkBook 16+ 2025 锐龙 AI 9 365 版笔记本开售：32G + 1T 售 7999 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/799/998.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/799/998.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 06:55:37 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 10 月 3 日消息，2025&nbsp;款联想&nbsp;ThinkBook&nbsp;16+&nbsp;锐龙版笔记本现已正式开售，这款笔记本搭载“AMD&nbsp;锐龙&nbsp;AI 9 365&nbsp;处理器&nbsp;+ 32GB RAM + 1TB&nbsp;存储空间”配置，<strong>售&nbsp;7999&nbsp;元</strong>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1258" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/2aa993a0-5931-4c80-8935-779a7708cdd0.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 ThinkBook 16+ 2025 锐龙 AI 9 365 版笔记本开售：32G + 1T 售 7999 元" width="924" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1214" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/d371d29d-56a7-4436-afdd-6e1c19729726.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 ThinkBook 16+ 2025 锐龙 AI 9 365 版笔记本开售：32G + 1T 售 7999 元" width="734" /></p><p>该机机身采用全金属打造，整体重量约&nbsp;1.9 千克，厚度&nbsp;16.9mm，机身支持&nbsp;180&nbsp;度开合，内置&nbsp;85Whr&nbsp;电池，通过&nbsp;MIL-STD-810H&nbsp;标准认证。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="886" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/c698d456-5297-4c9f-a8d4-7405b8775e3d.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 ThinkBook 16+ 2025 锐龙 AI 9 365 版笔记本开售：32G + 1T 售 7999 元" width="738" /></p><p>性能方面，IT之家获悉该机搭载&nbsp;10&nbsp;核心&nbsp;20&nbsp;线程&nbsp;AMD&nbsp;<strong>锐龙&nbsp;AI 9 365&nbsp;</strong>处理器，采用&nbsp;32GB&nbsp;<strong>板载</strong>&nbsp;LPDDR5x 7500MHz RAM&nbsp;及&nbsp;1TB PCIe Gen 4 SSD，使用双风扇散热，性能释放&nbsp;65W。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="760" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/2742660f-f382-495a-a4c9-6b53a5538dc0.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 ThinkBook 16+ 2025 锐龙 AI 9 365 版笔记本开售：32G + 1T 售 7999 元" width="740" /></p><p>该机配备&nbsp;16&nbsp;英寸&nbsp;3200×2000 分辨率&nbsp;165Hz 面板，通过德国莱茵&nbsp;TÜV&nbsp;硬件低蓝光认证和&nbsp;TÜV eyesafe&nbsp;认证，亮度&nbsp;400&nbsp;尼特。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1240" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/8e11bd02-4afa-4e9b-908a-23e5afaa32a3.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 ThinkBook 16+ 2025 锐龙 AI 9 365 版笔记本开售：32G + 1T 售 7999 元" width="714" /></p><p>该机支持&nbsp;Wi-Fi 7&nbsp;技术，左置&nbsp;1&nbsp;个&nbsp;USB-C 3.2 Gen 2&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个&nbsp;USB-A 3.1&nbsp;接口、&nbsp;1&nbsp;个&nbsp;HDMI 2.1&nbsp;接口、&nbsp;1&nbsp;个&nbsp;USB4&nbsp;接口、1&nbsp;个 3.5mm&nbsp;音频接口；右置&nbsp;1&nbsp;个&nbsp;RJ45&nbsp;网口、1&nbsp;个&nbsp;USB-A 3.1&nbsp;接口、&nbsp;1&nbsp;个&nbsp;MicroSD&nbsp;读卡器、1&nbsp;个&nbsp;USB-A 2.0&nbsp;接口。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="568" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/10/6d6f90ec-cf2b-43d6-b46e-f1ec21d59418.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 ThinkBook 16+ 2025 锐龙 AI 9 365 版笔记本开售：32G + 1T 售 7999 元" width="1004" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/LgnWGMd" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/95629/30/52191/82387/66f388f9F30986899/4da1a8851f6fe92b.jpg" title="联想 ThinkBook 16+ 2025 锐龙 AI 9 365 版笔记本开售：32G + 1T 售 7999 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">联想 ThinkBook 16+ 2025 锐龙 AI 9 365 笔记本</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 7999 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
